channel.title: First RSPS
channel.description:
Hello, I have played RSPS's for about 2 years now, and finally decided to try to make my own. I will most likely not make it public, but will just make it for myself. There are a few questions/requests I have:
-What is a good client+source that has: Chaotics, d claws, korasi, bosses, ect? -I would like to be helped out with whatever server you guys think is the best.
Thanks, Ain
